title: Lenovo Legion 5 AMD Ryzen 7 5800H 16GB DDR4 1TB NVME SSD RTX 3060 6GB 15.6 IPS 165Hz 100% sRGB Display Windows 10
description:
Legion 5 Gen 6 (15” AMD) Gaming Laptop

Battle-ready performance
Up to AMD Ryzen™ 7 5800H mobile processors 
Up to NVIDIA® GeForce RTX™ 30 series graphics
15" FHD display featuring amazing color accuracy and Dolby Vision™
Nahimic 3D audio and the Legion Truestrike keyboard

Experience the top AAA games on the Lenovo Legion 5. Inside the clean minimalist chassis of the Legion 5 is everything you will ever need to compete on equal footing with the pros including the latest generation AMD Ryzen processor and NVIDIA GeForce RTX graphics for performance that is AI-optimized by the Legion AI Engine powering the revolutionary Legion Coldfront 3.0 and Q Control. Excel across every AAA title with a 15 inch FHD display at up to 165 Hz refresh rate featuring 100 percent sRGB color accuracy. Plus relish the new Nahimic 3D audio and the legendary Legion TrueStrike keyboard so you can strike with pinpoint precision. Enjoy purpose-built performance on the Legion 5 available in Phantom Blue.
MANUFACTURERS DESCRIPTIONPower and minimalism with Lenovo LegionLegion 5 15 offers tons of options for every player. Its minimalist casing houses a powerful AMD Ryzen processor and NVIDIA GeForce graphics  and Legion Coldfront 2.0 watches over their appropriate temperature. The stunning refresh rate on the FHD screen with 100% color fidelity and the fast control of the TrueStrike keyboard will leave rivals far behind.
Playing with GeForce RTX ™. RTX is a serious game.Extremely fast and quiet operation. Real-time ray tracing and graphics enhanced by artificial intelligence. And on top of that the mobility of the slimmest and lightest structures in the world. Its all thanks to the NVIDIA Turing ™ GPU architecture and the breakthrough RTX platform. Now you can show what you can do - only on a GeForce RTX gaming laptop.
A cold front is approachingLegion 5 15 takes the bold steps where others dare to combine industry-leading thermal efficiency with any configuration you choose. The perfectly tuned Coldfront 2.0 cooling system dissipates heat through a dual-channel thermal mechanism with 67 liquid crystal polymer-coated fan blades with copper tubing. This will leave your rivals far behind with Q Control 3.0s manual selection of Quiet Sustainable and Competitive thermal modes. Turbocharging also offers the Dual Burn function which squeezes the maximum power from the CPU and GPU during the game.
Power and concentrationLegion 5 15 helps you stay in the arena wherever you are so it has a battery that lasts all day and an intelligent discharge power management system. It is powered by an elegant and small power supply with Rapid Charge Pro technology which replenishes the charge from 0 to 50% in less than half an hour. In hybrid mode the dedicated graphics card is disabled outside of games and Q Control 3.0 allows you to use Quiet Mode lowering the CPU voltage so you can concentrate longer on working without power from the outlet.
A sonic advantageThe Legion 5 15 emits loud deep bass sound through the Harman Kardon® 2W speaker system. Dolby Atmos® technology works with the headphones and produces an immersive three-dimensional sound that comes from all sides with surprising clarity and depth for complete immersion in any game environment. This way you gain an advantage in games because by locating individual sounds you can accurately track all threats - including those lurking above and behind you.

About Us
Our story began in Dec 2011 when internet penetration in Nepal was just about 9%. Yet we were encouraged to start not just a company but an ecommerce industry that would have a significant impact in Nepal’s economy for generations to come. Bootstrapped with just Rs.50000 we rented a small garage worked on broken furniture and chairs and worked hard to build a strong company and significantly contributing in building an ecommerce industry. Today  Sastodeal  is one of the leading ecommerce companies in Nepal with millions of customers and thousands of vendors / partners all over Nepal. description:
Amazon Alexa for your PC
With Alexa on your PC you can simplify your life and use your voice to get more done. Stay organized with shopping lists to-do lists and reminders. Watch the news listen to music control your smart home from the comfort of your couch video call with friends and family and more. With Alexa Show Mode you can use your PC as a full-screen interactive experience that features rich visuals and lets you talk to Alexa from across the room.



Smarter convenience


Optimize your time and effort with smart features designed to streamline your day. Enjoy up to 18 hours of battery life thanks to Intelligent Cooling that optimizes performance based on your needs. Need something? Just ask Alexa now featuring an improved UI and expanded features. Navigate your desktop intuitively with the optional pen and fly through the web via the ultra-fast connectivity of WiFi 6—the Yoga 6 2 in 1 laptop is built for best-in-class connectivity and mobility.


Connect securely
Encased in the Yoga 6’s chassis are features that enhance security including a privacy shutter that makes your webcam physically hacker-proof and a fingerprint reader that recognizes only you for instant login.

title: Lenovo ThinkPad X13 AMD Ryzen 5 Pro 4650U / 16GB RAM / 512GB SSD / 13.3" FHD Display (Optical Mouse And Bag Free)
description:
Go-anywhere performance


At less than ¾" thin and weighing only 1.29kg / 2.84lbs the ThinkPad X13 is a thin and light laptop that is easy to take wherever you go—without sacrificing performance to get there. With up to 10th Gen Intel® Core™ i7 processing plus up to 16GB DDR4 memory and 1TB of high-speed PCIe SSD storage this laptop has speed and power.




Last longer between charges


The ThinkPad X13 laptop gives you all-day battery performance further enhancing its portability. Once you need more power rapid-charging technology gives you 80% in just an hour.





Always ready


With Modern Standby your ThinkPad X13 laptop will wake in one second and connect online one second later. Its Wake On Voice feature allows you to wake it via voice command from across the room—as long as the lid is open.




Keep your private info private


Protect your data and yourself with enhanced ThinkShield features like ThinkShutter—a physical cover for the webcam—and an improved optional PrivacyGuard screen that helps prevent nosy neighbors from reading your screen. Log in with one finger via the optional match-on-chip fingerprint reader and let the discrete Trusted Platform Module (dTPM) 2.0 chip encrypt your hardware.




Stay connected everywhere



The ThinkPad X13 laptop keeps you online wherever you go. WiFi 6 enables fast and steady connections even on crowded public platforms or choose the optional LTE-A card that provides connection wherever there’s cellular service*. Even phone connections are easier to manage thanks to the new functions on the F9-F11 keys—easily call answer or hang up with just the touch of a finger.

title: Asus VivoBook Flip 14 TP412FA i3 10th Gen / 4GB RAM / 256GB SSD / 14" FHD 360 Touch display / Stylus Support
description:
Mobility Slim stylish lightweight ASUS VivoBook Flip 14 is thinner and lighter than ever — with an amazingly thin 17.6mm profile it weighs just 1.5kg2. Its one of the most portable 14-inch convertible laptops around keeping you productive and entertained — anywhere.



Screen
NanoEdge display
With an ultra-narrow 6.15mm NanoEdge bezel design the VivoBook Flip 14 fits a 14-inch Full HD display into a typical 13-inch laptop frame with an incredible 82% screen-to-body ratio for more immersive viewing. The display also features 178˚ wide-view technology to ensure that colors and contrast remain vivid and bold even when viewed at sharp angles.



Amazing performance
VivoBook Flip 14 is powered by up to an Intel® Core™ i7 processor with up to 8GB DDR4 RAM for smooth multi-tasking performance. With up to 1TB SSD storage the VivoBook Flip 14 has more than enough space for your photo albums and multimedia libraries. And with ultra-fast dual-band 802.11ac Wi-Fi you can enjoy speeds up to 6x faster than 802.11n3!

Touch
Think it write it!
VivoBook Flip 14 is designed for the ultimate touch experience and detects the subtlest movements of your fingertips. Its high-precision touch sensors are spaced at 6mm intervals — this ensures greater sensitivity over displays with the industry standard 9mm spacing between sensors. VivoBook Flip also supports ASUS Pen so you can let your creativity flow with a natural responsive feel.
